```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many safety pins are in the image?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many safety pins are in the image?')

ANSWER3=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER1} >= 5')
ANSWER4=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER2} xor {ANSWER3}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER4)
```
